short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Search for candidates on Linkedin and quickly import them to your Keywork.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With only a click this tool will import and associate a candidate linkedin profile, his photo and his resume to a job position in Keywork. 

Keywork is a time-saver tool oriented for digital talent and staffing business management.
